// Classroom scene example

// Load educational extension
LOAD EXTENSION educational

// Setup environment
ADD ENVIRONMENT CLASSROOM

// Draw teacher
DRAW TEACHER WITH AGE 40 AND PROFESSIONAL_ATTIRE AT LEFT

// Draw students in grid layout
DRAW STUDENT WITH AGE 10 AT GRID 1, 1
DRAW STUDENT WITH AGE 11 AT GRID 2, 1
DRAW STUDENT WITH AGE 10 AT GRID 3, 1
DRAW STUDENT WITH AGE 11 AT GRID 1, 2
DRAW STUDENT WITH AGE 10 AT GRID 2, 2

// Export
EXPORT AS PNG WITH RESOLUTION: 1024x768

